title: Hartigan bats in three to lead No. 7 Tech past JMU, 11-8 - VT hokiesports.com
content: Hartigan bats in three to lead No. 7 Tech past JMU, 11-8  VT hokiesports.com
description: Led by fifth-year transfer Conor Hartigan's three-RBI night against his former team on Wednesday, the No. 7 Virginia Tech baseball team outlasted James Madison, 11-8, during the teams' back-and-forth affair at English Field at Atlantic Union Bank Park.
